text: The 2016 Thailand Open Grand Prix Gold will be the 14th grand prix's badminton tournament of the 2016 BWF Grand Prix Gold and Grand Prix. The tournament will be held at Nimibutr Stadium in Bangkok in Thailand 4–9 October 2016 and had a total purse of $120,000. ==Men's singles== ===Seeds=== # Ihsan Maulana Mustofa (First Round) # Sony Dwi Kuncoro (Final) #
